# Stepnoy, Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Stepnoy () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 113 as of 2010. There are 7 streets.
Geography
Stepnoy is located 49&nbsp;km northeast of Mukhorshibir (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tugnuy is the nearest rural locality.
